# mc-tracker Design System

Use Tailwind utilities with `cn()` / CVA. Define theme tokens in `src/styles.css` (`@theme`, CSS variables) — don't scatter one-off hex values in components.

**Font:** Geist Variable (`@fontsource-variable/geist`).

**Dark mode:** class-based — `.dark` on `<html>`. Variant: `@custom-variant dark (&:where(.dark, .dark *));`

**Default border:** `border-color` uses `--color-monitor-gray-200` in dark / `--border` semantic token.

---

## Design Tokens

### Brand / Accent (`monitor-*`)

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `monitor` / `primary` | Primary accent (light) — `#6b16ed` |
| `monitor-50` | Highlighted button bg (light) |
| `monitor-100` | Highlighted hover (dark), scrollbar thumb |
| `monitor-200` | Highlighted button text (light) |
| `warning` / `primary` (dark) | Primary accent in dark mode — `#fcd452` |

### Neutral surfaces (`monitor-gray-*` / shadcn semantic)

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `base` / `background` (dark) | Page background — `#101010` |
| `monitor-gray-100` / `card` (dark) | Component background |
| `monitor-gray-200` / `border` (dark) | Elevated surface / borders |
| `monitor-gray-300` | Input borders, hover overlays |

### Semantic

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `success` | Online / healthy — `#22c55e` |
| `error` / `destructive` | Offline / errors — `#dc2626` |
| `warning` | Accent (dark), caution states |

### Radius

| Token | Usage |
|-------|-------|
| `rounded-snug` (6px) | Buttons, inputs, dense controls |
| `rounded-soft` (10px) | Cards, dashboard panels |
| `rounded-sm` / `rounded-lg` | shadcn defaults where already used |

### Accent swap (light vs dark)

| Context | Light | Dark |
|---------|-------|------|
| Primary accent | `monitor` / `text-monitor` | `warning` / `text-warning` |
| Focus ring | `ring-monitor` | `ring-warning` |
| Link variant | `text-monitor` | `text-warning` |
| Spinner | `text-monitor` | `text-warning` |

### Chart colors

Use `--chart-1` … `--chart-12` from `styles.css` via `chart-colors.ts` — don't hardcode series colors in components.

---

## Typography

Body: `text-sm antialiased`. Muted text: `text-muted-foreground`.

**Headings and card titles** must stay readable in dark mode — use `text-foreground` or `dark:text-white` on titles; don't leave headings at default muted gray.

---

## Components

Use CVA variants (`default`, `highlighted`, `brand`, `destructive`, etc.) — not string flags with switch chains. Match existing `src/components/ui/` implementations.

### Buttons

- Default: `border-border bg-card` with muted hover.
- Highlighted: `border-monitor bg-monitor-50 text-monitor-200` (light); `dark:bg-monitor/20 dark:hover:bg-monitor-100` (dark).
- Focus: `focus-visible:ring-monitor dark:focus-visible:ring-warning` with `ring-offset-background dark:ring-offset-base`.

### Cards / dashboard

- Use shadcn `Card` or `DashboardCard` patterns — `rounded-soft`, `bg-card`, `border-border`.
- Metric charts: `MetricChartCard` + deferred hydration via chart hooks.

### Forms / auth

- Auth pages use `AuthPageShell` + `AuthForm` layout.
- Inputs follow shadcn `Input` / `Label` with monitor focus tokens.

### Toasts

- `sonner` via `Toaster` in `__root.tsx` — `richColors closeButton`.

---

## Styling rules

- Merge with `cn()`; prefer token classes (`bg-monitor-gray-100`, `text-warning`) over raw hex.
- Avoid inline `style` for static colors/spacing — exception: uPlot canvas sizing and computed chart dimensions.
- Icons: `lucide-react`, `size-4` default in buttons unless `size` variant overrides.
- Destructive admin actions: `Dialog` confirmation before delete; toast on success.

---

## Implementation notes

- Extend `src/styles.css` `@theme` / `:root` / `.dark` when adding tokens — map shadcn semantic vars (`primary`, `card`, `border`) to monitor values.
- shadcn components: override variants via CVA; keep Radix behaviour, swap visual classes.
- Composition over one-off markup — reuse `DashboardCard`, `MetricChartCard`, `LoadingState` when patterns repeat.
